---
// Pipeline Section - The Client Journey
---

<section class="section-premium" style="background-color: var(--color-secondary);">
  <div class="container-premium">
    
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <span class="text-xs font-display tracking-widest uppercase mb-4" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">The Pipeline</span>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-8" style="color: var(--color-primary);">
        How a Stranger Becomes a Client<br>and a Client Becomes a Referral
      </h2>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Pipeline Flow -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Flow Visualization -->
      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Vertical Timeline -->
        <div class="absolute left-8 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 h-full w-0.5" style="background-color: var(--color-border);"></div>
        
        <!-- Pipeline Steps -->
        <div class="space-y-16">
          
          <!-- Discovery -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="absolute left-8 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 rounded-full border-4 border-white z-10" style="background-color: var(--color-accent);"></div>
            <div class="ml-20 md:ml-0 md:flex md:items-center md:gap-8">
              <div class="md:w-1/2 md:text-right md:pr-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Discovery</h3>
                <p class="mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">A business owner finds the tool through search, word of mouth, or a referral.</p>
                <span class="text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">Timeline: Ongoing</span>
              </div>
              <div class="hidden md:block md:w-1/2"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Self-Diagnosis -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="absolute left-8 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 rounded-full border-4 border-white z-10" style="background-color: var(--color-accent);"></div>
            <div class="ml-20 md:ml-0 md:flex md:items-center md:gap-8">
              <div class="hidden md:block md:w-1/2"></div>
              <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Self-Diagnosis</h3>
                <p class="mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">They enter their URL and see their own results. Most will fail three or more checks.</p>
                <span class="text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">Timeline: 30 minutes</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Contrast -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="absolute left-8 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 rounded-full border-4 border-white z-10" style="background-color: var(--color-accent);"></div>
            <div class="ml-20 md:ml-0 md:flex md:items-center md:gap-8">
              <div class="md:w-1/2 md:text-right md:pr-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Contrast</h3>
                <p class="mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">They see a site built by this business with all six checks green. They feel the gap themselves.</p>
                <span class="text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">Timeline: 1-2 hours</span>
              </div>
              <div class="hidden md:block md:w-1/2"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Enquiry -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="absolute left-8 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 rounded-full border-4 border-white z-10" style="background-color: var(--color-accent);"></div>
            <div class="ml-20 md:ml-0 md:flex md:items-center md:gap-8">
              <div class="hidden md:block md:w-1/2"></div>
              <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Enquiry</h3>
                <p class="mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">They reach out. The conversation begins with shared understanding of the problem.</p>
                <span class="text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">Timeline: 24-48 hours</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Proposal -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="absolute left-8 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 rounded-full border-4 border-white z-10" style="background-color: var(--color-accent);"></div>
            <div class="ml-20 md:ml-0 md:flex md:items-center md:gap-8">
              <div class="md:w-1/2 md:text-right md:pr-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Proposal</h3>
                <p class="mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">Simple, clear, defined scope and outcome. No ambiguity. Repeatable structure.</p>
                <span class="text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">Timeline: 2-3 days</span>
              </div>
              <div class="hidden md:block md:w-1/2"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Build -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="absolute left-8 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 rounded-full border-4 border-white z-10" style="background-color: var(--color-accent);"></div>
            <div class="ml-20 md:ml-0 md:flex md:items-center md:gap-8">
              <div class="hidden md:block md:w-1/2"></div>
              <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Build</h3>
                <p class="mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">Full stack. Astro, Sanity, Schema, Lead Layer. No shortcuts regardless of project size.</p>
                <span class="text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">Timeline: 2-4 weeks</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Delivery -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="absolute left-8 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 rounded-full border-4 border-white z-10" style="background-color: var(--color-accent);"></div>
            <div class="ml-20 md:ml-0 md:flex md:items-center md:gap-8">
              <div class="md:w-1/2 md:text-right md:pr-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Delivery</h3>
                <p class="mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">Tool verification on handover day. Every check green. Before and after documented.</p>
                <span class="text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">Timeline: 1 day</span>
              </div>
              <div class="hidden md:block md:w-1/2"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Referral Ask -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="absolute left-8 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 rounded-full border-4 border-white z-10" style="background-color: var(--color-accent);"></div>
            <div class="ml-20 md:ml-0 md:flex md:items-center md:gap-8">
              <div class="hidden md:block md:w-1/2"></div>
              <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Referral Ask</h3>
                <p class="mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">One specific, direct ask at the moment of successful delivery.</p>
                <span class="text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">Timeline: Immediate</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Check-In -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="absolute left-8 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 rounded-full border-4 border-white z-10" style="background-color: var(--color-accent);"></div>
            <div class="ml-20 md:ml-0 md:flex md:items-center md:gap-8">
              <div class="md:w-1/2 md:text-right md:pr-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Check-In</h3>
                <p class="mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">Quarterly light touch. Results update. Relationship stays warm and active.</p>
                <span class="text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">Timeline: Quarterly</span>
              </div>
              <div class="hidden md:block md:w-1/2"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Next Referral -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="absolute left-8 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 rounded-full border-4 border-white z-10" style="background-color: var(--color-accent);"></div>
            <div class="ml-20 md:ml-0 md:flex md:items-center md:gap-8">
              <div class="hidden md:block md:w-1/2"></div>
              <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Next Referral</h3>
                <p class="mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">The cycle continues with new discovery through trusted recommendation.</p>
                <span class="text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">Timeline: Ongoing</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Key Insights -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-32">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-primary mb-4">Why This Pipeline Works</h3>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid-premium grid-premium-3">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-display font-bold text-primary mb-2">Self-Qualification</h4>
          <p class="text-secondary text-sm">
            The tool does the selling. Prospects arrive already understanding their problem and the solution.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-display font-bold text-primary mb-2">No Sales Pitch</h4>
          <p class="text-secondary text-sm">
            The conversation starts with shared understanding, not education or persuasion.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-display font-bold text-primary mb-2">Relationship-Driven</h4>
          <p class="text-secondary text-sm">
            The relationship continues because value is ongoing, not because contracts force it.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="text-center mt-32">
      <div class="inline-block p-12 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-premium-lg max-w-2xl">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-primary mb-4">Ready to Start Your Journey?</h3>
        <p class="text-secondary mb-8">
          Begin with a free technical assessment of your current website. See exactly where you're losing customers.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-4">
          Get Your Free Assessment
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
  </div>
</section>
